{"tid":1750681,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"無論今次區選贏定輸，都證明左一樣嘢","createTime":"2019-11-24T13:06:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T04:04:57.000Z","uid":277273,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3947dd7f08eb6b600f784416efbce3c4af9e18b8","tid":1750681,"uid":277273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:06:38.000Z","msg":"今天戰果無論係泛民、建制、本土、素人邊一邊贏都好，無論你係勇武、和理非、港豬，無論你係黃、係藍、係紅、係黑、係中立都好，<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人今日區選既高投票率證明左一件事！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地值得、應該、準備好擁有雙普選！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n由6月到現在<br />\n一百萬、二百萬零一遊行，區選投票破二百萬人，反映左香港人有非常高既公民意識，無論你投邊一邊，<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢一種覺醒代表我地廣泛市民認同民主選舉</span></span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n係腐敗制度下，我地仍然<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">寸土不讓地向政權用盡一切努力表達個人訴求</span></span>，今日見到好多年輕人不著黑衫、不戴口罩去投票，係咪代表我地停止抗爭？唔係呀！<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地唔係認同、滿足於現在的選舉制度</span></span>，因為單係今次區議會已經有好多限制、好多黑幕，但點都好，點解我地仲要出黎投票？因為我地都想透過今日的區選，話俾全世界既人知，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地有足夠覺醒、有公民質素去提名、去一人一票選出屬於香港人既特首</span></span>！當其他民主國家台灣2016年總統選舉投票率66.27%；美國2016年總統選舉投票率56.9%；係香港截至19:30 已經有63.65%！ 香港人係配得同應該要有民主！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">從來都係極權獨裁政府拒絕我地、打壓我地，令我地唔能夠以和平的方式抗爭、係政府教識我地和平遊行無用</span>，係政府不斷以DQ候選人、分組點票、比例代表制等的方式令香港的選舉變得不民主。所以<span style=\"color: red;\">呢幾個月我地先會用盡各種方法抗爭</span>！今日我地就話比所有人知，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人係識、而且好熱衷於和平地表達訴求</span></span>！ <br />\n<br />\n真正令香港走上抗爭之路的，從來都係政府！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應承我，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論今日區選結果係點！</span></span>我地都不滿足與此啊！<br />\n因為我地<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">未贏、未贏、未贏</span></span>啊！<br />\n我地要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">真正的普選</span></span>，我地要五大訴求逐一實現！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1SVwwK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1SVwwK.png&h=7d55caed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1dfcaf9f440c3a28930da603aace03666e5d0c5","tid":1750681,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68bdf190699b3b27af66f7b5dba1d09f7a5e92f2","tid":1750681,"uid":317505,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:08:27.000Z","msg":"打完今日飛機就繼續抗爭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da7a490d26c31964593e1ffb769ae1bdc9e6cb9","tid":1750681,"uid":19984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:16:35.000Z","msg":"打得飛機多對身體唔好，一齊努力做返啲正經野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea7b0b828bc8c22dc30e3a6f7fd40123c0b29ca","tid":1750681,"uid":308769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:24:28.000Z","msg":"好有道理<br />\np牌無力一推"},{"pid":"ff142faf49e42aeae8c54b63a12ddc63e2d6d555","tid":1750681,"uid":142708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T14:06:40.000Z","msg":"好文大力推<br />\n民主之路的確漫長<br />\n但我地都唔可以放棄<br />\n因為堅持先睇到希望<br />\n各位手足撐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4673cf1dfbdecf956079aa4196173cfa41d434","tid":1750681,"uid":272030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T14:08:24.000Z","msg"